
Interview Project ReadingIsGood

Project is build with microservices in mind and consider to be used by other microservices or a frontend written in react or similar framework.
Project is developed upon Spring Boot (and its sub helper packages) and utilises MongoDb as database. Also Lombok library is used for convenience and brevity.
End product can be launched with regular java executable commands and with also maven's "spring-boot:run" goal.
After launching the app you can navigate to "/swagger-ui/index.html" to check 'api end points' exposed by the app.

-----Config-----
Consider modifying the below parameters according to your system

-application.properties
    -spring.data.mongodb.database=*
    -spring.data.mongodb.port=*
    -spring.data.mongodb.host=*
